data.description: Welcome to this beautifully updated four-bedroom,  two bath home situated on a spacious corner lot! As you step inside you will appreciate the grand dining room that has room for everyone! The cozy fireplace in the living room is perfect to gather around with family and friends on those chilly days. This home also features a large two car garage that is perfect for storing vehicles and much more. Don't miss the chance to make this well-cared-for home your own!
